headline: Molina Healthcare (MOH) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of healthcare insurance company Molina Healthcare (NYSE:MOH) jumped 2.5% in the morning session after the stock appeared to stage a technical rebound following a sharp decline in late July.
